categories: Default Category/Shopping Bags/Frosted Plastic Bags/Frosted Plastic Merchandise Bags
name: Bag Merch Clear Frost 9x12
description:
Frosted SOS (SOS - Square Opening Sacks) Hi Density Gift Bags with Bottom Card Inserts available in Clear Frosted and Colored Frosted and are one of the hottest packaging ideas for use in your retail store. These bags are made of thick Hi Density plastic which gives them their frosted color and extra strength. 
    Clear Frosted SOS bags are available in 8 different sizes.  Two sizes do not have die cut handles (3 1/2" x 2" x 7" and 4" x 2 1/4" x 9 3/4" packed 500 per case).  All other Clear Frosted SOS bags have a convenient die cut handle and are packed either 125, 200 or 250 per case depending upon the size of the bag.  Clear Frosted SOS bags vary in thickness from 3 to 4.5 mil. 
    Colored Frosted Hi Density Bags like below are made of 4 and 5 mil thick Hi Density plastic and have convenient die cut handles. They are packed: 500, 250 and 125 per case as indicated.

name: Bags T-Shirt 12x9x23 "Enjoy"
description:
An Environmentally
Responsible Choice

 






Enjoy! T-Shirt Bag Features:

  • 12"x9"x23"
  • Better quality and gage for reusability
  • Strong handles
  • Economical
  • Flexible sides that expand
  • 1,000 bags per case

These bags are made with 25% post-consumer recycled (PCR) material.

Plastic Bags:

  • Are re-used by consumers for many purposes which saves the production of another bag
  • Weigh approximately 75% less than equivalent paper bags so they use less resources to transport
  • Use approximately 40% less energy to produce than the equivalent paper bag
  • Generate approximately 80% less solid waste than the equivalent paper bag
  • Require approximately 91% less energy to recycle than the equivalent paper bag
  • Are often made with post-consumer recycled material
  • Are 100% recyclable: lowering the amount of plastic entering landfills and using new resources
  • Take up approximately 10% of the landfill space of the equivalent paper bag
  • Produce no greenhouse gas in decomposition
  • Produce less water pollution in manufacturing
  • Produce less air pollution in manufacturing
  • Are produced from the by-products of refining gasoline, so not using this by-product is the irresponsible thing to do

These plastic bags are an environmentally friendly choice for your green retail packaging needs!
